OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781885473
OL,3,CRare giraffe welcomed to zoo to save
OL,4,Cspecies from extinction
OL,6,FA rare northern giraffe has arrived at
OL,7,Fa zoo in hopes he will have calves and
OL,8,Fhelp improve the conservation breeding
OL,9,Fprogramme.
OL,11,FKris, a lively three-year-old-male,
OL,12,Fhas travelled to Chester Zoo from West
OL,13,FMidlands Safari Park to meet the zoo's
OL,14,Fresident female herd.
OL,16,FHis introduction has been carefully
OL,17,Fplanned, with conservationists
OL,18,Fmatching the animal based on genetics,
OL,19,Fage, and temperament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
