OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781885473
OL,3,CRare giraffe welcomed to zoo to save
OL,4,Cspecies from extinction
OL,6,FFewer than 7,000 northern giraffes
OL,7,Fremain in the wild due to habitat
OL,8,Floss, poaching, and conflict with
OL,9,Fhumans.
OL,11,FRosie Owen, giraffe keeper at Chester
OL,12,FZoo, said: "Kris' arrival marks the
OL,13,Fbeginning of an important new chapter
OL,14,Ffor the herd here at Chester.
OL,16,F"He's already settling into his new
OL,17,Fhome brilliantly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781885473
OL,3,CRare giraffe welcomed to zoo to save
OL,4,Cspecies from extinction
OL,6,F"At just over three years old, Kris is
OL,7,Fstill a young giraffe, but he's full
OL,8,Fof confidence and is already getting
OL,9,Fto know the herd ` and out of his five
OL,10,Fnew housemates, four of them are older
OL,11,Ffemales who are all considerably
OL,12,Ftaller than him.
OL,14,F"He's taking everything in his stride
OL,15,Fand we're optimistic that, in time,
OL,16,Four matchmaking will pay off and he'll
OL,17,Fgo on to play a vital role in helping
OL,18,Fto save his species from extinction."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
